  "texts": [
    "While most SSLNS-TD algorithms perform standard train/dev/test dataset splitting, recent work curates larger and higher-quality datasets.",
    "OpenTabs (Ye et al, 2023) released around 2,000 unlabeled datasets.",
    "TP-BERTa (Yan et al, 2024; Ye et al, 2023) released 202 labeled and 145 unlabeled datasets derived from OpenTabs.",
    "UniTabE (Yang et al, 2024) released 283,000 unlabeled datasets.",
    "The open-source effort to standardize pretraining datasets further accelerates research in SSL4NS-TD."
  ],
